                    Global movement across wallets, payouts, and QR purchases.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <button
                  type="button"
                  onClick={() => loadTransactions(token)}
                  className="flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400"
